## 8) Run pg_rewind

### Rewind from source server connection

```bash
sudo tee /run/pgvm/op.env >/dev/null <<'EOF'
PG_RW_PGMAJOR=16
PG_RW_BIN_DIR=/usr/pgsql-16/bin
